*Prvi* put sam izašla u grad. (This was the first time I went out to the city.)

*Prvog* dana je postao njen najbolji prijatelj. (On the first day he became her best friend.)

Ona je *prva* otišla u školu. (She was the first one to go to school.)

*Prvih* nekoliko dana bilo je izuzetno naporno. (The first few days were extremely tiring.)

*Prvom* susretu je bila veoma uplašena. (She was very scared on their first meeting.)